{"tid":2225452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"吳秋北街站派月餅賀10.1 近百人零距離排隊涉違限聚令","createTime":"2020-10-01T10:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T10:48:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fcce5c0327fe1ba1ad3104fc3569e1a745fa90f6","tid":2225452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"早前有報道引述建制派消息，中聯辦下令建制派今日（1日）於各區「大搞」慶祝活動，包括派月餅、集合一同唱國歌及揮動國旗等，營造慶祝國慶的熱烈氣氛。其中，多個親中團體今早（1日）於北角設街站派月餅、食油等，吸引大批市民排隊領取。工聯會會長吳秋北亦有現身北角街站，惟被《眾新聞》拍攝連同他在內，已有至少5人，涉違犯4人限聚令。《眾》記者向吳秋北問及現場大量人群聚集，會否擔心違反限聚令，吳沒有回應，僅聲稱每個街站只有4名工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/ATWY6A5TRJHNPP2MW3AJG3LRTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FATWY6A5TRJHNPP2MW3AJG3LRTI%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w10cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=177641d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FATWY6A5TRJHNPP2MW3AJG3LRTI%2F&h=9ea76654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/ATWY6A5TRJHNPP2MW3AJG3LRTI/</a>"},{"pid":"8f02a338d04d19efc0ee058511262d6b9690e751","tid":2225452,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27715a40682da4d493589aab510b8b3e60c30bec","tid":2225452,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"點解冇人報公安？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6029f263521567c664dd0842e8d14f98a495a8e9","tid":2225452,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27715a40682da4d493589aab510b8b3e60c30bec","tid":2225452,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"點解冇人報公安？<img sr